stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Active: bootstrap (loaded from SM secret)
    Active --> Previous: rotation (PutSecretValue, Watch fires)
    Previous --> [*]: overlap window expires (>= longest live token TTL)

    Active: signs new JWTs (active kid), published in JWKS
    Previous: verify-only, still in JWKS for cached tokens

    note right of Active
        Emergency revocation does not rotate the key.
        It uses the JTI denylist instead.
    end note
